      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, representing the pinnacle of care and maintenance. The exterior paint retains its original factory luster without a single scratch or swirl mark, and the interior remains in showroom state, still smelling like new with no signs of wear on the leather or controls. Mechanically, it is absolutely perfect; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at the dealership, and all systems function exactly as they did the day it rolled off the lot. For a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives like it just left the showroom, this is an unparalleled opportunity.",
